-- Quid state treasury controller
--
-- This program is intentionally practical and narrow:
--   * view treasury and supply figures
--   * print money into treasury
--   * grant treasury funds to an account
--   * burn money from treasury
--   * view account balances
--
-- It is not the citizen terminal and not the economic dashboard.
-- =============================================================================

